name: Alpha Five Set Data Dictionary Memo File
summary: Memo file created by Alpha Five, an IDE that enables users to develop Web, desktop, and mobile applications; contains data in the memo format, which is the same format used by .FPT and .DDM files; includes design information and code for any objects, reports, and forms attached to the set; created along with .SET and .SEX linked set files.
